---
import Pepper3D from "../../components/InteractiveAreas/Pepper3D.astro";

---

<section class='flex flex-col justify-center items-center py-16' id='Heart'>
  <h3 class="title">Wife</h3>
  <div class="h-full " >
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-center text-xl" translate="no">Virginia <strong class="text-white" translate="no">"Pepper" </strong> Potts</p>
    <Pepper3D/>
    <p class='text-gray-300 text-center px-4 '>As her relationship with Stark developed, their personal bond grew stronger, and they eventually became a couple. In addition to her executive work, Pepper Potts has also been involved in "Iron Man" adventures, contributing to his intelligence and bravery in crisis situations.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  code {
		font-family:
			Menlo,
			Monaco,
			Lucida Console,
			Liberation Mono,
			DejaVu Sans Mono,
			Bitstream Vera Sans Mono,
			Courier New,
			monospace,
			'IRON MAN OF WAR';
	}

  @font-face {
    font-family: 'IRON MAN OF WAR';
    src: url(../../public/IRON\ MAN\ OF\ WAR\ 002\ NCV.ttf);
    font-weight: normal;
    font-style: normal;
    font-display: swap;
  }

  p {
		font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
    max-width: 500px;
	}

	.title {
		color: #7cdaf9;
		font-family: 'IRON MAN OF WAR';
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 3rem;
		line-height: 1;
		animation: pulse 2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite;
	}

	@keyframes pulse {
		50% {
			opacity: .5;
		}
	}
</style>